            <ul>
	      <li><a href="http://bookworm.culturomics.org/OL/" target="_blank">OpenLibrary</a> open domain books</li>
              <li><a href="http://bookworm.culturomics.org/arxiv/" target="_blank">ArXiV</a> science puplications</li>
              <li><a href="http://bookworm.culturomics.org/ChronAm/" target="_blank">Chronicling America</a> historical newspapers</li>
              <li><a href="http://bookworm.culturomics.org/congress/" target="_blank">US Congress</a> bills, amendments, and resolutions</li>
              <li><a href="http://bookworm.culturomics.org/ssrn/" target="_blank">Social Science Research Network</a> research paper abstracts</li>
