          <h4><strong>More Bookworms!</strong></h4>
          <p>View bookworms made by collaborators using
            <ul>
              <li><a href="http://benschmidt.org/profGender/" target="_blank">RateMyProfessor</a> teacher reviews by gender</li>
	      <li><a href="http://benschmidt.org/statenames/" target="_blank">Baby Names</a> US birth records</li>
	      <li><a href="http://bookworm.library.yale.edu/collections/vogue/" target="_blank">Vogue</a> fashion and beauty archives</li>
              <li><a href="http://movies.benschmidt.org/" target="_blank">Movies</a> dialogues of movie and TV shows</li>
              <li><a href="http://benschmidt.org/poli/2015-SOTU" target="_blank">Speeches</a> State of the Union addresses<br>[<a href="http://benschmidt.org/poli/SOTU" target="_blank">word cloud version</a>]</li>
	      <li><a href="http://bookworm.htrc.illinois.edu/" target="_blank">HTRC</a> public domain texts from HathiTrust Digital Library</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
